<p>(责编：刘泽、张雪冬) </p>
➜闲置地变“增收园”
http://www.sohu.com/a/417001830_114731	6145
<p align="center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200908/80a4ac2f3a994dba95d2b36e7717503a.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">科技特派员指导田召小果树种植技术。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200908/df91a793182b45a79b3f44d9f020062b.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">硕果累累。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200908/770191c76347424d887c624831f255c5.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
